# Local development secrets for the video-detection demo.
# Copy to `.dev.vars` (gitignored) and fill in if you want to exercise the
# scheduled usage-report email locally. Not needed for the camera/detection demo.

# API token with "Account Analytics: Read" — used by the scheduled() handler to
# query the Analytics Engine SQL API for the monthly/daily usage reports.
# In production, set this with: npx wrangler secret put AE_SQL_API_TOKEN
AE_SQL_API_TOKEN=
